" for this file being automatically read by the Tridactyl Firefox Addon
" the Traidactyl 'native messenger' must be installed
" cf. https://github.com/tridactyl/tridactyl/wiki/Exemplar-.tridactylrc-files


" use better search key bindings
" cf. https://github.com/tridactyl/tridactyl/issues/64#issuecomment-496913151
"
bind / fillcmdline find
bind ? fillcmdline find -?
bind n findnext 1
bind N findnext -1
bind ,<Space> nohlsearch


